name: ARTCHICK.SWAG
description: This art is dedicated to artchick.eth (https://twitter.com/digitalartchick) who has been a boon to this NFT space and no amount of words are enough to thank her for the support she is giving to the artists and the good vibes she spread through her tweets. We all thank you from the bottom of our heart and let us wish that she keeps on shining like a crazy diamond.
